'''Alfred Kastil''' [ka:stil] (May 12, 1874, [[Graz]] – July 20, 1950, [[Schönbühel]]/Danube, [[Niederösterreich]]) was an [[Austrians|Austrian]]-[[Germany|German]] [[philosopher]].
He taught as a [[professor]] at the [[Innsbruck University]] (1912-1933).
